<div class="cv__statement">
<h3>Personal Statement</h3>
<p>With over 10 years of experience in creative services — including 8+ years specializing in eCommerce — I craft intuitive, visually engaging, and high-performing user interfaces for enterprise-level online platforms. My expertise lies in translating complex business requirements into elegant front-end experiences that enhance usability, accessibility, and conversion.</p>

<p>I’ve led the front-end implementation of large-scale eCommerce migrations, including moving a 20-year-old business from a legacy system to a modern SaaS platform integrated with a custom ERP via API connector. On BigCommerce Enterprise, I’ve delivered tailored B2B solutions featuring advanced UI customizations, customer-specific catalogues, and dynamic pricing — all built with a strong focus on responsive design, performance optimization, and modern development practices.</p>

<p>Passionate about clean, semantic code and cutting-edge technology, I follow the latest web standards to build scalable, maintainable, and future-ready interfaces that elevate the overall digital experience and drive measurable business growth.</p>
